---

"Karvey" is an Ona/Selknam word meaning *Afán* (zeal / drive).

Karvey synthesizes Mauricio Quezada Ibáñez's (HainTech) own experience with
conceptual ideas from the Kiro (spec-driven development / cc-sdd) and gstack
(Garry Tan) methods. It is a synthesis and conceptual inspiration; it does NOT
incorporate code from those projects.

